title: Anatomy Primal 3D Interactive Series 3. Hands
description:
=============================================================================
      Complete Human Anatomy Primal 3D Interactive Series (9 CD-ROMs)
=============================================================================


Complete human anatomy now available, in 3D with Primals Interactive series
of 9 Cd-Roms.
An inexhaustible resource in my ongoing studies, as well as in patient
education
The best interactive training tool on the market
I use the Cds with nearly every patient

Includes 9 CD-Roms:

    * Interactive Hand
    * Interactive Pelvis:Male & Female
    * Interactive Foot & Ankle
    * Interactive Head and Neck
    * Interactive Hip
    * Interactive Knee 1.1
    * Interactive Spine
    * Interactive Shoulder
    * Interactive Thorax & Abdomen


Benefits

    * Explain injuries, conditions and treatments more effectively with this
      accurate visual tool.
    * Aid your interpretation of MR by comparing the 3D model with MR slices
      in three planes.
    * Save time when you have this vast image resource for presentations,
      hand outs etc.
    * Make teaching and learning enjoyable!

Installing:
1. Insert your iso file into your virtual cd drive, then install program interactive head and neck or other from the primal3D series
2. Run program and learn!
3. That&#039;s it! It works.

I will upload all of the 9cd roms and therefore please keep seeding!!
Ulysses56
